test_cases.title: Successful password reset
test_cases.given: User is on the login page AND has a registered account
test_cases.then: User receives a password reset link via email

test_cases.title: Password reset fails due to invalid token
test_cases.given: User is on the login page AND has a registered account
test_cases.when: User enters an invalid password reset token

test_cases.title: Password reset fails due to non-existent email
test_cases.given: User has a registered account with an invalid email address
test_cases.then: Error message 'Account not found' is displayed

test_cases.title: Password reset fails due to empty password field
test_cases.given: User is on the login page AND has a registered account
test_cases.when: User leaves password field empty and clicks Reset Password button
test_cases.then: Validation error message 'Password cannot be empty' is displayed

test_cases.title: Successful password reset with new password
test_cases.given: User has a registered account AND has an active password reset token
test_cases.when: User enters new password and confirms it on the password reset page
test_cases.then: User is redirected to login page WITH session created
